    "Context file and endpoint URL are distinct concerns: `esr use` stores `ws://HOST:PORT/adapter_hub/socket`, while runtime_bridge talks to `/handler_hub/socket` via discover_runtime_url — adapter hub vs handler hub are two separate Phoenix endpoints on esrd.",
